WEBVTT

00:01.050 --> 00:02.295
EDDIE: Previously on "The Path"...

00:02.296 --> 00:04.225
ISIAH: Where you headed this late?

00:04.226 --> 00:06.235
CAL: Couldn't sleep.
Thought I'd take a drive.

00:06.236 --> 00:09.255
Cal is reckless, and he will
bring the movement down.

00:09.256 --> 00:11.135
No one has seen him since last night.

00:11.136 --> 00:12.185
SARAH: Silas...

00:12.186 --> 00:14.085
It does resemble one of his.

00:14.086 --> 00:15.205
What is it doing here?

00:15.206 --> 00:19.065
Marriage is a cornerstone
of The Movement.

00:19.066 --> 00:20.295
If you forgive me, I want that.

00:20.296 --> 00:24.115
What did you do to get Ashley
to break up with Hawk?

00:24.116 --> 00:25.255
You had him do it?

00:25.256 --> 00:29.075
ABE: Your Light is not going
to help my kid get better.

00:29.076 --> 00:30.135
Forget The Light.

00:30.136 --> 00:32.134
Just do not give up on your kid.

00:32.136 --> 00:34.105
Your husband left a journal.

00:34.106 --> 00:36.135
Why wasn't it given to the police?

00:36.136 --> 00:38.265
SARAH: I think you'll
understand when you read it.

00:38.266 --> 00:40.215
ISIAH: Can I help you?

00:40.216 --> 00:41.275
EDDIE: You know, everyone
says that they have

00:41.276 --> 00:44.265
these big moments on the walk.

00:44.266 --> 00:46.165
They see Truth.

00:46.166 --> 00:48.075
The truth is, I didn't.

00:48.076 --> 00:50.065
Program won't work for him. He's gone.

00:50.066 --> 00:51.165
CAL: Steve finished the rungs.

00:51.166 --> 00:53.135
He wants you to help
shape the next phase

00:53.136 --> 00:54.195
of The Movement with me.

00:54.196 --> 00:56.205
I believe in the work that we do,

00:56.206 --> 01:00.165
but the rest is just
fucking fairy tales.

01:00.166 --> 01:02.165
You're talking about everything...

01:02.166 --> 01:04.205
everything in my soul.

01:04.206 --> 01:07.065
You don't actually believe that.

01:07.066 --> 01:08.166
You don't know me.

01:10.276 --> 01:13.275
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

